# 6dff3d4b4f3d42ab966ee410c8d77027
#: ../../developer-guide/api/functions/TSHttpHdrHostGet.en.rst:34
msgid ""
"Get the host for the request. :arg:`bufp` and :arg:`offset` must "
"reference an HTTP request header. A pointer to the host is returned and "
"the length is stored in the ``int`` pointed at by :arg:`length`. Note the"
" returned text may not be null terminated. The URL in the request is "
"checked first then the ``Host`` header field."
msgstr ""

# bbf17fd8be29463da55e7cd1b347e57b
#: ../../developer-guide/api/functions/TSHttpHdrHostGet.en.rst:42
msgid ""
"This is much faster than calling :c:func:`TSHttpEffectiveUrlStringGet` "
"and extracting the host from the result."
msgstr ""

